get_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https://wa.me/6293089724?text=Tenho%20interesse%20em%20receber%20um%20orcamento\" id=\"facaumorcamento\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">faça um orçamento</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15fc4dc e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"15fc4dc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-27b2373 e-con-full elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"27b2373\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0fc4827 e-transform elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"0fc4827\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_transform_flipX_effect&quot;:&quot;transform&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"667\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2149397553.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1454\" alt=\"A ideal Soluções Anticorrosivas, especialistas em pintura industrial e revestimentos anticorrosivos de alto desempenho.\" srcset=\"https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2149397553.webp 667w, https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2149397553-200x300.webp 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0cf5fa4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0cf5fa4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0ce2561 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0ce2561\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Principais <font color=\"#0B80DF\">Vantagens.</font></h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f5e9c6d elementor-icon-list--layout-inline elementor-list-item-link-full_width elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-list\" data-id=\"f5e9c6d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items elementor-inline-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Antederrapante</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Antederrapante</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Resistencia elevada</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Impermeável</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e09d018 elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e09d018\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"242\" data-end=\"333\"><strong>Piso Industrial em Uretano: Alta Resistência Térmica, Química e Mecânica para Ambientes Severos.</strong></p><p data-start=\"411\" data-end=\"843\">O <strong data-start=\"413\" data-end=\"443\">piso industrial em uretano</strong>, também conhecido como <strong data-start=\"467\" data-end=\"501\">piso de poliuretano cimentício</strong>, é uma solução de revestimento de altíssimo desempenho, projetada para suportar condições extremas de operação. Esse sistema é ideal para áreas que exigem <strong data-start=\"657\" data-end=\"760\">resistência mecânica elevada, variações térmicas severas e contato com produtos químicos agressivos</strong>, garantindo durabilidade, segurança e excelente custo-benefício ao longo do tempo.</p><p data-start=\"845\" data-end=\"1146\">Com formulação à base de <strong data-start=\"870\" data-end=\"896\">poliuretano cimentício</strong>, o piso em uretano forma uma superfície extremamente <strong data-start=\"950\" data-end=\"981\">rígida, densa e impermeável</strong>, sendo amplamente utilizado em <strong data-start=\"1013\" data-end=\"1145\">indústrias alimentícias, frigoríficos, cervejarias, cozinhas industriais, laboratórios, farmacêuticas e áreas com tráfego pesado</strong>.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2dc9052 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2dc9052\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fc9ecf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8fc9ecf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 data-start=\"1148\" data-end=\"1192\">Vantagens do piso industrial em uretano:</h4><ul data-start=\"1193\" data-end=\"1654\"><li data-start=\"1193\" data-end=\"1278\"><p data-start=\"1195\" data-end=\"1278\"><strong data-start=\"1195\" data-end=\"1223\">Alta resistência térmica</strong>: suporta variações de temperatura entre -40°C a +120°C</p></li><li data-start=\"1279\" data-end=\"1335\"><p data-start=\"1281\" data-end=\"1335\"><strong data-start=\"1281\" data-end=\"1335\">Excelente resistência a impactos e abrasão intensa</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1400\"><p data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1400\"><strong data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1400\">Superfície antiderrapante e segura para ambientes molhados</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1475\"><p data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1475\"><strong data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1475\">Boa resistência química contra ácidos, solventes, álcalis e gorduras</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1528\"><p data-start=\"1478\" data-end=\"1528\"><strong data-start=\"1478\" data-end=\"1528\">Impermeabilidade total e facilidade de limpeza</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1529\" data-end=\"1580\"><p data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1580\"><strong data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1580\">Longa vida útil mesmo em ambientes agressivos</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1581\" data-end=\"1654\"><p data-start=\"1583\" data-end=\"1654\"><strong data-start=\"1583\" data-end=\"1654\">Aplicável com inclinação para escoamento, ideal para áreas laváveis</strong></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1656\" data-end=\"1932\">A <strong data-start=\"1658\" data-end=\"1667\">Ideal</strong> realiza projetos completos de instalação de <strong data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1732\">pisos em uretano</strong>, com avaliação técnica do ambiente, escolha da espessura e acabamento mais adequado, garantindo total conformidade com as exigências da <strong data-start=\"1869\" data-end=\"1931\">ANVISA, MAPA e normas sanitárias e de segurança industrial</strong>.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17b18ec e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"17b18ec\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5eb2fd6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5eb2fd6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5589583 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5589583\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Obras <font color=\"#0B80DF\">Realizadas.</font></h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-767edaf e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"767edaf\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9454bc9 gallery-spacing-custom elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-gallery\" data-id=\"9454bc9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-gallery.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-gallery\">\n\t\t\t<div id='gallery-3' class='gallery galleryid-623 gallery-columns-5 gallery-size-medium'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"9454bc9\" data-elementor-lightb